{"tid":1464203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［散水警報］好多散水撚想大家唔好搞機場呀","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:50:19.000Z","uid":72650,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8082debf4d1a1b81dd693d071031b636025793","tid":1464203,"uid":72650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:35:44.000Z","msg":"睇黎有人諗唔到計點拆塞機場，開始要用埋啲咩影響到旅客去叫大家散水。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">戇鳩影響唔到你既話我塞黎把撚呀？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n講咩唔好去離境大堂呀，搞到旅客呢啲戇鳩野先係分化撚！又要好似5年前咁討論番邊個最開心邊個唔開心呀？法國地鐵罷工你去求佢唔好影響你呀笨，戇鳩鳩<br />\n<br />\n敵人反對，即是我們做對了！"},{"pid":"9f1422726f05fc3966901818d214820960540138","tid":1464203,"uid":72650,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:36:41.000Z","msg":"所有散水撚都係分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f90d5f7e45c537b8b07234762b79f4b0b9c52e","tid":1464203,"uid":127751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"108336d6ab7e82aa3ca52a8832da304f8af6621b","tid":1464203,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:39:59.000Z","msg":"係想形造到決定停飛果個係政府唔係我哋啫，公關上會好好多<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"d9d574ec17d7cc9b230703fefc9b156c20d24feb","tid":1464203,"uid":72650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"拒絕散水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets